These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, chef
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the security-guard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | woodworking       | baking |
| Job         | chef | security-guard  |
| Sport       | rugby    | swimming    |
| Transport   | taxi       | scooter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, drama
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, basketball
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the journalist is on the far left##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Job           | journalist | paramedic      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | fantasy      |
| Sport         | rugby | basketball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, 7up
There 2 different types of food: peas, corn
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, metal
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, scooter
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking water is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person eating peas is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | water | 7up  |
| Food          | peas    | corn   |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | house   |
| Transport     | scooter     | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
