3. the person drinking fanta is the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | lemonade       | fanta |
| Food          | carrot         | apple    |
| Job           | dancer | entrepreneur    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel           | jazz   |

