2 different pets are kept: horse, dog
1. the american is the owner of the dog##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the american is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | nectarine | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | classical      |
| Nationality   | chinese | american    |
| Pet           | horse    | dog    |

