.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, lawyer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, scientific
2 different pets are kept: ferret, dog
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, trike
1. the chef is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the chef is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | lawyer | chef     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance          | scientific |
| Pet           | ferret          | dog    |
| Transport     | trike            | taxi       |

 